title: Gosper's Lambert series identities of level $14$
abstract:
We derive two Gosper's Lambert series identities of level $14$ which involve
the $q$-constant $\Pi_q$ using a special case of Bailey's $_6\psi_6$ summation
formula and certain propeties of $\eta$-quotients and generalized
$\eta$-quotients on the congruence subgroup $\Gamma_0(14)$.
